<H3>Combinazione di RDR e NAT</H3>
d340 1
a340 1
<P>
d344 10
d355 1
a355 10
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<TT>rdr on $int_if proto tcp from $int_net to $ext_if port 80 
  -&gt; \<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$server <BR>no nat on $int_if proto 
tcp from 
  $int_if to $int_net<BR>nat on $int_if proto tcp from $int_net to 
$server port 
  80 -&gt; \<BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$int_if </TT>
</BLOCKQUOTE>

